    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Geth's response is the correct one. Uncles do not maintain a list of transactions that are included (they are part of the block body, nto the header (which an uncle is)).\r\n\r\nReturning `transactions: []` would imply that the block corresponding to the uncle contained no transactions, which is most probably false.",
